    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, dissolve your <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> in 750ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[975ml]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [1.4L]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>– this is your <strong>vegetable stock</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1680278276357-x200.jpg",
