    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the tomato is starting to blister, add your <strong>tomato paste </strong>and <strong>chopped garlic </strong>to the pan with your <strong>dried oregano </strong>and 1 tsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> [2 tsp] </span><strong>sugar</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and cook for 1-2 min or until fragrant</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
