      "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, add your <strong>arborio rice </strong>and cook for 1 min, stirring to coat the grains in the oil</p><p>Add the <strong>vegetable stock</strong> a ladle at a time, stirring continuously for 25-30 min or until all of the stock is absorbed and the rice is cooked</p>",
